{"tid":54834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[live] 一條毒撚既11日澳洲探險","createTime":"2016-12-26T00:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T00:27:43.000Z","uid":59905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c7457ff5e5bd9e03f3056152d2f55395ad95b8","tid":54834,"uid":59905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T00:27:43.000Z","msg":"廢話少講, 頭幾日會留係brisbane, 之後再出發去gold coast<br />\n<br />\n落機已經係夜晚2330, 由於小弟係一條毒撚既關係, 所以住係backpacker house<br />\n<br />\nday 1:  目的地係lone pine<br />\n食個早餐就出發, 7 仔買既三文治, 成5aud真係貴到hihi, 係香港可以食個全餐... <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/suohnl80\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsuohnl80&h=c6577edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後買巴士飛去目的地, 買飛果陣唔係好似地鐵咁揀目的地就搞掂, 要自已揾個目的地再認佢係咩zone , 再比錢, 結果小弟不材買錯左, 好彩巴士司機個呀嬸特赦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tci6gr3m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftci6gr3m&h=1499c2d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去之前我做過功課, 呢個lone pine庇護所 係平得黎, 你又可以同d動物好close, 任你同d動物玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4hvg0pae\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4hvg0pae&h=fc199c4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p9no3bcd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp9no3bcd&h=b5296d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呢個園入面, 你行行吓會見到d小動物, 有火雞, 小蜥蜴咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7ndakhuj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7ndakhuj&h=2fe8f5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而大型既動物就要住係特定園區, 但遊客自由進出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備去抱樹熊 , 轉頭再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}